reviewText: these movies were a 14th birthday present for my daughter.  2 great "chick flicks"  just fun, happy movies to sit down and enjoy together over a bowl of popcorn!
Thank you.  It is a Christmas present but she will love it.
They were born funny with little twist of comedy drama
Love these movies. my daughter and I watch them at least twice a month.
I love the Wedding Planner and not so much My Best Friends. However they are both well made for what they are. I recommend this selection as good weekend fun Enjoy!
I love these movies and they came in great condition! They are definitely worth buying together as a combo! Best girls movie night ever!
Best mix ever, it was also the best present for my sister. It got here fast and was in time for Christmas. Thanks.
